/*------------------------------------------------------------------
 MBlue Simple-Gray Sidebar (Ver. 0.3.5)
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Author: M.BLUE - Tested on: Firefox 3.0.1 - Last Update: 26.07.2008
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:
 Transforms the sidebar to integrate better with the Simple-Gray
 Theme.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
What it does:
 - Gives the sidebar (better if using AIOS) the Simple-Gray look
 - Skins the Bookmarks & History when opened inside the sidebar
 - Makes the AIOS Top-Sidebar-Toolbar Tabs-like
 - Sidebar thin splitter (2 versions to choose)
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Supported Extensions:
 All-in-One Sidebar, Tab Sidebar, TagSifter, QuickNote.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Notes:
All-in-One Sidebar: This Style is optimized to use only a few of
 the features of AIOS. To make it work well, open the AIOS Options
 and disable all the extra Toolbars features. You should also
 disable Multipanel, Error Console and extra panels cause they are
 useless and looks bad inside the sidebar. Only the download and
 Bookmarks/History Panels should be enabled. Enable the Extension
 Panel when using the "Simple-Gray Slim-Extension" for better
 results.

Downloads: If you want your downloads to be in the sidebar, you
 should use the "Simple-Gray Slim-Download" Style to integrate it
 better in the Sidebar.

Extension-list: If you want the Extensions List to be in the sidebar,
 you should use the "Simple-Gray Slim-Extension" Style to integrate
 it better in the Sidebar.

More Extensions: You can use this in combination with the
 Simple-Gray Sidebar Ext-Support to skin some extension that opens
 in the sidebar.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Integrates with:
 MBlue Simple-Gray Theme
 MBlue Simple-Gray Theme Ext-Support
>MBlue Simple-Gray Sidebar
 MBlue Simple-Gray Sidebar Ext-Support
 MBlue Simple-Gray Slim-Download
 MBlue Simple-Gray Slim-Extension
 MBlue Simple-Gray Buttons
 MBlue Simple-Gray Top-Toolbar
 MBlue Simple-Gray Popup
 MBlue Simple-Gray Statusbar Icon
 MBlue Combine Nav-Buttons Vista
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Updates:
 26.07.2008 Ver. 0.3.5 = new version
 18.07.2008 Ver. 0.3.1 = working on new version
 15.07.2008 Ver. 0.2.7 = small fixes
 10.07.2008 Ver. 0.2.6 = small fixes
  8.07.2008 Ver. 0.2.5 = code splitted
  5.07.2008 Ver. 0.2.3 = optimized the thin splitter (2 versions)
  4.07.2008 Ver. 0.2.2 = updated some backgrounds
  3.07.2008 Ver. 0.2.1 = adjusted splitters and borders
  2.07.2008 Ver. 0.2.0 = added support for the Extension View
  1.07.2008 Ver. 0.1.8 = fixed bookmarks and history panels,
                         added a new tabs background,
                         optimized Tab Sidebar and TagSifter
 30.06.2008 Ver. 0.1.5 = added the thin splitter,
                         optimized Quicknote layout,
                         code optimized
 29.06.2008 Ver. 0.1.4 = removed useless items from the AIOS menu,
                         optimized TagSifter layout
 28.06.2008 Ver. 0.1.3 = optimized layout, changed some backgrounds
 27.06.2008 Ver. 0.1.2 = added QuickNote support,
                         optimized layout for All-in-One Sidebar
 25.06.2008 Ver. 0.1.1 = added All-in-One Sidebar support
 20.06.2008 Ver. 0.1.0 = Tab Sidebar and TagSifter support
------------------------------------------------------------------*/



/******************************************************************* 
 Change the Sidebar Header background
*******************************************************************/

sidebarheader, 
#aiostbx-toolbar-sidebarheader {
-moz-appearance: none !important;
background: #eeeeee 
url("data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAAYCAMAAAAMEmfoAAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAABtQTFRF/v7+9vf38vHx+/v88O/v9PT0+vn5////7u7uUjqi4AAAAB9JREFUeNpiYGeAQQYGZgY2BkYGVgYmBhYGDuwQIMAADQoAmX1OdUQAAAAASUVORK5CYII=") repeat-x top !important;
}



/******************************************************************* 
 Sidebar thin splitter gray (Ver.1) (Active)
*******************************************************************/



#sidebar-splitter{
-moz-appearance: none !important;
-moz-border-top-colors: none !important;
-moz-border-bottom-colors: none !important;
-moz-border-left-colors: none !important;
-moz-border-right-colors: none !important;
background-color: #eeeeee !important;
width: 1px !important;
padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px !important;
border-left: solid 0px #aaaaaa !important;
border-right: solid 1px #999999 !important;
margin-left: 0px !important;
margin-top: 0px !important;
}

#sidebar-splitter:hover{
border-color: #e2f2fb !important;
outline: solid 1px #888888 !important;
}



